#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:1
msgid "Panoramica"
msgstr "Overview"

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:3
msgid "Scopo"
msgstr "Purpose"

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:5
msgid ""
"Disegnare un istogramma di un campione sperimentale, con opzioni per "
"evidenziare la media, la fascia `+- 1 sigma`, la legenda, la griglia e il"
" salvataggio della figura."
msgstr ""
"Draw a histogram of an experimental sample, with options to highlight the"
" mean, the `+- 1 sigma` band, the legend, the grid, and figure saving."

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:7
msgid "Parametri"
msgstr "Parameters"

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:9
msgid "`x`: dati da istogrammare."
msgstr "`x`: data to histogram."

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:10
msgid "`ddof`: parametro passato a `standard_deviation` per la banda."
msgstr "`ddof`: parameter passed to `standard_deviation` for the band."

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:11
msgid ""
"`style`: `None` usa gli `rcParams` correnti, `\"mespy\"` carica lo stile "
"del package, qualunque altra stringa viene passata a Matplotlib come nome"
" stile."
msgstr "`style`: `None` uses the current `rcParams`, `\"mespy\"` loads the package style, and any other string is passed to Matplotlib as a style name."

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:12
msgid "`bins`: numero di bin, algoritmo automatico o array dei bordi."
msgstr "`bins`: number of bins, automatic algorithm, or array of edges."

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:13
msgid ""
"`bin_width`: larghezza fissa dei bin. Non puo essere usata insieme a "
"`bins` diverso da `\"auto\"`."
msgstr ""
"`bin_width`: fixed bin width. It cannot be used together with `bins` "
"other than `\"auto\"`."

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:14
msgid "`hist_range`: coppia `(xmin, xmax)` usata come range dell'istogramma."
msgstr "`hist_range`: `(xmin, xmax)` pair used as the histogram range."

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:15
msgid "`label`, `xlabel`, `ylabel`, `title`: etichette testuali."
msgstr "`label`, `xlabel`, `ylabel`, `title`: text labels."

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:16
msgid ""
"`show_bin_ticks`, `tick_rotation`, `decimals`: controllano la "
"formattazione dell'asse x. `decimals` deve essere un intero compreso tra "
"0 e 20."
msgstr "`show_bin_ticks`, `tick_rotation`, and `decimals`: control x-axis formatting. `decimals` must be an integer between 0 and 20."

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:17
msgid ""
"`show_mean`, `show_band`, `show_legend`, `show_grid`: attivano o "
"disattivano elementi del grafico."
msgstr ""
"`show_mean`, `show_band`, `show_legend`, `show_grid`: enable or disable "
"plot elements."

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:18
msgid "`xlim`, `ylim`: limiti espliciti degli assi."
msgstr "`xlim`, `ylim`: explicit axis limits."

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:19
msgid "`ax`: asse matplotlib esistente da riusare."
msgstr "`ax`: existing matplotlib axis to reuse."

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:20
msgid ""
"`figsize`, `dpi`, `save_path`: parametri di creazione e salvataggio della"
" figura. `figsize` e `dpi` vengono passati alla creazione della figura "
"solo quando esplicitati."
msgstr "`figsize`, `dpi`, and `save_path`: parameters for creating and saving the figure. `figsize` and `dpi` are passed to figure creation only when explicitly provided."

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:21
msgid ""
"`title_fontsize`, `title_pad`, `legend_fontsize`, `legend_loc`: override "
"puntuali di titolo e legenda. Se lasciati a `None`, la funzione usa lo "
"stile attivo."
msgstr "`title_fontsize`, `title_pad`, `legend_fontsize`, and `legend_loc`: targeted overrides for the title and legend. If left as `None`, the function uses the active style."

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:22
msgid ""
"`bar_color`, `edgecolor`: override puntuali dei colori delle barre. Se "
"lasciati a `None`, la funzione usa i valori forniti da stile o "
"`rcParams`."
msgstr "`bar_color` and `edgecolor`: targeted overrides for bar colours. If left as `None`, the function uses the values supplied by the active style or `rcParams`."

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:23
msgid ""
"`mean_color`, `band_color`, `hist_alpha`, `band_alpha`, `grid_alpha`, "
"`mean_symbol`: controllano linea della media, banda `+- 1 sigma`, "
"trasparenze e simbolo in legenda. `grid_alpha=None` lascia la griglia "
"allo stile attivo."
msgstr "`mean_color`, `band_color`, `hist_alpha`, `band_alpha`, `grid_alpha`, and `mean_symbol`: control the mean line, the `+- 1 sigma` band, transparency, and the legend symbol. `grid_alpha=None` leaves the grid to the active style."

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:25
msgid "Restituisce"
msgstr "Returns"

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:27
msgid ""
"Una tupla `(fig, ax)` con figura e asse su cui e stato disegnato "
"l'istogramma."
msgstr ""
"A `(fig, ax)` tuple with the figure and axis on which the histogram was "
"drawn."

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:29
msgid "Errori ed eccezioni"
msgstr "Errors and exceptions"

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:31
msgid ""
"`ValueError` se `x` e vuoto, non monodimensionale o contiene valori non "
"finiti."
msgstr ""
"`ValueError` if `x` is empty, not one-dimensional, or contains non-finite"
" values."

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:32
msgid ""
"`ValueError` se `xlim`, `ylim` o `hist_range` non sono coppie valide di "
"valori finiti."
msgstr ""
"`ValueError` if `xlim`, `ylim`, or `hist_range` are not valid pairs of "
"finite values."

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:33
msgid "`ValueError` se `hist_range` non soddisfa `xmin < xmax`."
msgstr "`ValueError` if `hist_range` does not satisfy `xmin < xmax`."

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:34
msgid "`ValueError` se `bin_width <= 0`."
msgstr "`ValueError` if `bin_width <= 0`."

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:35
msgid ""
"`ValueError` se `bin_width` e `bins` vengono usati insieme in modo "
"incompatibile."
msgstr "`ValueError` if `bin_width` and `bins` are used together incompatibly."

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:36
msgid "`ValueError` se `decimals` non e un intero valido tra 0 e 20."
msgstr "`ValueError` if `decimals` is not a valid integer between 0 and 20."

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:37
msgid ""
"`ValueError` se `figsize` non e una coppia positiva quando la figura "
"viene creata internamente."
msgstr ""
"`ValueError` if `figsize` is not a positive pair when the figure is "
"created internally."

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:39
msgid "Esempio"
msgstr "Example"

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:58
msgid "Note"
msgstr "Notes"

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:60
msgid ""
"Lo stile viene applicato tramite "
"[`_style_context`](../../../checks/plot_utils/style-context.md), lo "
"stesso helper usato anche da [`lin_fit`](../../fit_utils/lin-fit.md)."
msgstr "The style is applied through [`_style_context`](../../../checks/plot_utils/style-context.md), the same helper also used by [`lin_fit`](../../fit_utils/lin-fit.md)."

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:61
msgid "Se `ax` e `None`, la funzione crea una nuova figura con `plt.subplots`."
msgstr "If `ax` is `None`, the function creates a new figure with `plt.subplots`."

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:62
msgid "Se passi `ax`, la figura restituita e `ax.get_figure()`."
msgstr "If you pass `ax`, the returned figure is `ax.get_figure()`."

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:63
msgid ""
"La validazione dei limiti, delle dimensioni e di `decimals` passa per "
"[`_validate_axis_limits`](../../../checks/plot_utils/validate-axis-"
"limits.md), [`_validate_figsize`](../../../checks/plot_utils/validate-"
"figsize.md) e [`_validate_decimals`](../../../checks/plot_utils/validate-"
"decimals.md)."
msgstr "Validation of limits, figure size, and `decimals` goes through [`_validate_axis_limits`](../../../checks/plot_utils/validate-axis-limits.md), [`_validate_figsize`](../../../checks/plot_utils/validate-figsize.md), and [`_validate_decimals`](../../../checks/plot_utils/validate-decimals.md)."

#: ../../source/moduli/plot_utils/histogram/panoramica.md:64
msgid ""
"`save_path` salva sempre con `bbox_inches=\"tight\"`; il `dpi` viene "
"aggiunto al salvataggio solo quando e esplicitato."
msgstr "`save_path` always saves with `bbox_inches=\"tight\"`; `dpi` is added to saving only when it is explicitly provided."

